Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西条君  西条君人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓拓先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也快跟上去
