Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只会为了我自己的目的破坏Noah2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士都到齐了呢
