Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨深
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得全身是伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还那么勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叫你等着我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  我喜欢你
