Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要快救梨深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫西条拓巳
